dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Portage County, WI 2010
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Portage County, Wisconsin at 2010. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Portage_Hydro_2010. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Portage_HydroLine_2010' and 'Portage_HydroPoly_2010'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.co.portage.wi.gov/375/Land-Information-GIS
